{"tid":773353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「四電一腦」影響小 電腦節平貨料吸80萬客","createTime":"2018-08-09T12:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T12:56:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"177f92739b25257232ef7a7d0e4a95567b0d726c","tid":773353,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180809/20472182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F20472182&d=1pE96L4oep1cJqjzI4q3NCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9a2d6ca8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F20472182&h=8b9731c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180809/20472182</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月09日 <br />\n<br />\n「四電一腦」影響小<br />\n電腦節平貨料吸80萬客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180809/large/09la6p51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180809%2Flarge%2F09la6p51.jpg&h=41a80e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■科學園公司在電腦節記者會展示改良版機械人。方國成攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「香港電腦通訊節2018」於本月24至27日灣仔會展舉行，香港電腦商會創會會長張耀成表示，剛生效的「四電一腦」法例，對電腦產品影響最小，料業內不會因此而加價，強調「保證喺場內買嘅電腦價錢一定平過市場」。有電腦廠商稱，雖然新例增加每年逾百萬元成本，但不會轉嫁入場人士。有代理商則指，部分利潤微薄產品可能要加價。大會料，今年電腦節人流達到逾80萬人次，較去年升一成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180809/large/09la6p53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180809%2Flarge%2F09la6p53.jpg&h=038d0960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有參展商昨示範「擴增實境」（AR）手機遊戲。馬泉崇攝 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180809/large/a0804a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180809%2Flarge%2Fa0804a.gif&h=44ab7c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n$999買55吋OLED電視<br />\n<br />\n張耀成表示，今年電腦節有逾200個參展商，電腦產品受「四電一腦」法例影響最小，據了解業內很少因此加價，因電腦銷售周期亦短，加上在中美貿易戰影響下，電腦更出現減價情況，「保證喺場內買嘅電腦價錢一定平過市場」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，香港電器及電子設備回收協會於場內設環保回收站，鼓勵入場人士將棄置電腦或電子廢物進行回收，參與者可獲贈電腦節門票，去年成功回收300至400部電腦及周邊產品。<br />\n<br />\n華碩科技（香港）有限公司業務發展經理蕭嘉秀說，在新例下成本一定增加，「公司每年賣6至7萬部電腦，每部15蚊，都要成100萬」，又指每年額外支出或增至200至300萬元，令營運相對困難，但強調絕不將徵費轉嫁客人，因此產品定價不變。<br />\n<br />\n漢科電腦公司業務發展部總經理李沛鏗則稱，新例對一些利潤較低的產品會有加價壓力，「可能4,000蚊部電腦，轉嫁50蚊，作一部份行政費」，但電腦節以優惠吸客，故不會轉嫁有關徵費，期望生意較去年升10至20%。<br />\n<br />\n今屆電腦節將推出「激安大購賞」，Philips55吋 OLED4K Smart TV（原價27,980元）和ASUS TUF Gaming FX504電競電腦（原價13,9978元），激安價為999元，各限量1部。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n立志從醫「記住病人感受」16*小朋友自稱普通<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n4煞劫運鈔車掠1,000萬　司機遭爆樽頭破血流"},{"pid":"6d79aca2cc3ac44864aeb70e91d127d2f8ad7e45","tid":773353,"uid":3436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"俾30蚊入去幫人清舊貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f9155df63fe0e834e50df02f2adb571ca5c618","tid":773353,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年一度散貨場"},{"pid":"b0acd4c1412270bc2aff3d81a30d2d2e52354742","tid":773353,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"去電腦節=用幾千蚊幫人地處理垃圾"},{"pid":"a808680bb3ad685d48a80d15f01214b37f956e4d","tid":773353,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"水魚節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44008588269407175322adf3d424fcbd08222b56","tid":773353,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"清倉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b29fce721152833cc0aa6c40c9f89c47409037","tid":773353,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"回收電器？<br />\n<br />\n有入場卷換都ok"},{"pid":"f4c0eef29263008b2c5fc596ed0f6099ccc0700c","tid":773353,"uid":33438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"蟹貨展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}